                                        )

                                )

                            [attachment] => stdClass Object
                                (
                                    [required] => 
                                    [schema] => stdClass Object
                                        (
                                            [type] => array
                                            [items] => attachment
                                            [system] => attachment
                                        )

                                    [name] => Attachment
                                    [key] => attachment
                                    [hasDefaultValue] => 
                                    [operations] => Array
                                        (
                                        )

                                )

                            [issuelinks] => stdClass Object
                                (
                                    [required] => 
                                    [schema] => stdClass Object
                                        (
                                            [type] => array
                                            [items] => issuelinks
                                            [system] => issuelinks
                                        )

                                    [name] => Linked Issues
                                    [key] => issuelinks
                                    [autoCompleteUrl] => https://interfolio.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/picker?currentProjectId=&showSubTaskParent=true&showSubTasks=true&currentIssueKey=null&query=
                                    [hasDefaultValue] => 
                                    [operations] => Array
                                        (
                                            [0] => add
                                        )

                                )

                            [assignee] => stdClass Object
                                (
                                    [required] => 
                                    [schema] => stdClass Object
                                        (
                                            [type] => user
                                            [system] => assignee

                            [attachment] => stdClass Object
                                (
                                    [required] => 
                                    [schema] => stdClass Object
                                        (
                                            [type] => array
                                            [items] => attachment
                                            [system] => attachment
                                        )

                                        (

                            [issuelinks] => stdClass Object
                                (
                                    [required] => 
                                    [schema] => stdClass Object
                                        (
                                            [type] => array
                                            [items] => issuelinks
                                            [system] => issuelinks
                                        )

                                    [name] => Linked Issues
                                    [key] => issuelinks
                                    [autoCompleteUrl] => https://interfolio.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/picker?currentProjectId=&showSubTaskParent=true&showSubTasks=true&currentIssueKey=null&query=
                                    [hasDefaultValue] => 
                                    [operations] => Array
                                        (
                                            [0] => add
                                        )

                                )

                            [assignee] => stdClass Object
                                (
                                    [required] => 
                                    [schema] => stdClass Object
                                        (
                                            [type] => user
                                            [system] => assignee
                                        )

                                    [name] => Assignee

                                    [operations] => Array
                                        (
                                            [0] => set
                                        )

                                )

                        )

                )

            [9] => stdClass Object
                (
                    [self] => https://interfolio.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issuetype/10000
                    [id] => 10000
                    [description] => 
                    [iconUrl] => https://interfolio.atlassian.net/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=12000&avatarType=issuetype
                    [name] => Initiative
                    [subtask] => 
                    [expand] => fields
                    [fields] => stdClass Object
                        (
                            [summary] => stdClass Object
                                (
                                    [required] => 1
                                    [schema] => stdClass Object
                                        (
                                            [type] => string

                                        )

                                    [name] => Summary

                                )

                                        (
                                        )

                                    [allowedValues] => Array
                                        (
                                            [0] => stdClass Object

                                                    [self] => https://interfolio.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issuetype/10000

                            [attachment] => stdClass Object
                                (
                                    [required] =>

                                        (

                            [attachment] => stdClass Object
                                (
                                    [required] => 
                                    [schema] => stdClass Object
                                        (
                                            [type] => array
                                            [items] => attachment
                                            [system] => attachment

                                        (

                            [issuelinks] => stdClass Object
                                (
                                    [required] => 
                                    [schema] => stdClass Object
                                        (
                                            [type] => array
                                            [items] => issuelinks
                                            [system] => issuelinks
                                        )

                                    [name] => Linked Issues
                                    [key] => issuelinks
                                    [autoCompleteUrl] => https://interfolio.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/picker?currentProjectId=&showSubTaskParent=true&showSubTasks=true&currentIssueKey=null&query=
                                    [hasDefaultValue] => 
                                    [operations] => Array
                                        (
                                            [0] => add
                                        )

                                )

                            [assignee] => stdClass Object
                                (
                                    [required] => 
                                    [schema] => stdClass Object
                                        (
                                            [type] => user
                                            [system] => assignee
                                        )

                                    [name] => Assignee
                                    [key] => assignee
                                    [autoCompleteUrl] => https://interfolio.atlassian.net/rest/api/latest/user/assignable/search?project=PS&query=
                                    [hasDefaultValue] => 
                                    [operations] => Array
                                        (
                                            [0] => set
                                        )

                                )

                        )

                )

            [17] => stdClass Object
                (
                    [self] => https://interfolio.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issuetype/10107
                    [id] => 10107
                    [description] => This is the Xray Precondition Issue Type. Used to abstract common actions that must be ensured before the test case execution. A Precondtion can be associated with multiple test cases.
                    [iconUrl] => https://interfolio.atlassian.net/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=15678&avatarType=issuetype
                    [name] => Precondition
                    [subtask] => 
                    [expand] => fields
                    [fields] => stdClass Object
                        (
                            [summary] => stdClass Object
                                (
                                    [required] => 1
                                    [schema] => stdClass Object
                                        (
                                            [type] => string
                                            [system] => summary
                                        )

                                    [name] => Summary
                                    [key] => summary
                                    [hasDefaultValue] => 
                                    [operations] => Array
                                        (
                                            [0] => set
                                        )

                                )

                            [issuetype] => stdClass Object
                                (
                                    [required] => 1
                                    [schema] => stdClass Object
